<item>
            <title>[HBASE-297] hbase rest server should be started with hbase-daemon.sh</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-297</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, the hbase rest server is started with the hbase script.  But it should be started with the hbase-daemon script, which allows better configuration options.  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
